--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.1.1 (2019-05-31)
B: Create Docker configuration directory

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.0.1 (2019-05-13)
B: Remove double quotes for value in daemon.json by default

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-05-11)
C: Remove docker_max_concurrent_downloads and docker_max_concurrent_uploads options
F: Add docker_daemon option to configure daemon.json

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-05-10)
F: Add support for max-concurrent-downloads option (docker_max_concurrent_downloads)

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-10)
F: Add support for max-concurrent-uploads option (docker_max_concurrent_uploads)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-09-06)
F: Add support for HTTP_PROXY option (docker_http_proxy)
F: Add support for HTTPS_PROXY option (docker_https_proxy)
F: Add support for NO_PROXY option (docker_no_proxy)

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-04-19)
F: Initial release
